White has here as Black is wasting tempos with the bishop after all.} 10. Nc3
O-O 11. g3 $1 {[%cal Gc3a4,Gc4c5] quietly preparing the same Nc3-a4 and c4-c5
idea as we just analyzed after 9...Bc6. The pawn on h2 is now well defended
