f4 Bb7 13. Qc2 $14 {[%cal Gb2b3,Gc1b2,Gh2h4,Gg1h2,Gh4h5] White is clearly
better as he controls the center and has better positioned pieces.}) (11... Qc7
12. Be3 $14 {[%cal Gc4c5]}) (11... Be5 12. Na4 Qc7 13. Be3 d6 14. f4 Bf6 15. c5
d5 16. e5 Be7 17. Qc2 f6 18. Bd4 $16) 12. Na4 Qc7 13. c5 $14) 10. Nc3 O-O (
10... c5 {[%csl Rd4][%cal Rd7d6,Re7f6,Rg6e5,Re5c6] a typical plan - Black
