Qxd3 $14) 14. cxd5 cxd5 15. exd5 Bc5 16. Qe2 exd5 17. Nb5 Qb6 18. Bxc5 Qxc5+
19. Qf2 Qxf2+ 20. Rxf2 Ba6 21. Rd1 $14) (12... Nf4 13. Bc2 e5 $6 14. g3 Ne6 15.
f4 {[%cal Gf4f5,Gc2d3,Gd1d2,Gg3g4,Re6d4] with a dangerous kingside attack for
