17. Nd2 Be6 18. Kb1 a4 19. Qe3 a3 (19... b3 20. cxb3 axb3 21. a3 Red8 22. Nc1 {
[%cal Gd2c4]}) 20. b3 Nd7 21. Rdg1 {the direct f2-f4 breakthrough gives
