Qd2 (15. Rc1 $5) 15... Rad8 16. Rad1 d5 $11 {1-0 (61) Saric,I (2685)-Lalic,B 
(2396) Mali Losinj 2018}) (9... d5 10. Ba3 Ne6 11. Nc3 {[%csl Rc5][%cal Gc3a4]}
) 10. Bb2 d6 {probably the best setup for Black.} (10... d5 11. d3) (10... O-O
11. Nc3 f6 12. exf6 Bxf6 13. Rxe6 $1 dxe6 14. Qe2 {[%csl Rc5,Rc6,Re6,Re7][%cal
Ga1e1,Gc3a4] and Black will have great practical problems to hold this
position!}) 11. Nc3 Nd4 $1 12. exd6 Qxd6 13. Ne4 Qc7 14. Nxd4 cxd4 15. Ba3 O-O
16. d3 $11 {[%cal Gd1f3,Ge1e2,Ga1e1] the game is about equal but Black might
