(2511)-Popov,I (2608) Astana 2017})) (13... O-O 14. Bh6 {[%cal Gf3g5,Ga1d1,
Gc3e4,Ge4g5] again, White has a strong attack.}) 14. Bd2 $1 {[%cal Gc3e4,Gd2c3]
} O-O 15. Ne4 Qc7 16. Bc3 f6 {[%cal Re6f4,Re7e5] the only way to keep the game
sharp.} 17. Rad1 $14 {and White looks slightly better} (17. Qg3 Qxg3 18. hxg3
