[%cal Gf3h2,Gf2f4]}) 9. Nbd2 O-O 10. b4 {[%cal Gd2c4,Gd2b3,Gd1e1,Ge1c3]} Nd7
11. Nc4 b6 12. Qe1 Ba6 13. Qc3 Rae8 14. Re1 {[%cal Gc1b2,Gc3b3,Gb3a4]} *

